Invocation Name: division tutor
des:
Have Alexa help you learn division!

Simply launch the skill and tell Alexa the number you want to work on. She will generate ten division problems using that number. You can also ask for mixed numbers and she will generate random division problems using the numbers 2 through 9.

After ten problems, Alexa will give you a summary of your results and review any problems that you missed.

To launch, simply say, "Alexa, open Division Tutor."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
